 v1/ — original submission bundle
 v2/ — first revision
 ...
 unused/ — unused/excluded research artifacts
 ai_sessions/
 {session_id}/ — AI session logs, exported transcripts
 triage/ — literature triage exports
 supplementary/ — datasets, code, figures
