Authors can save drafts with missing transparency; publish requires
completeness.
Integrates with Workflows: check on transitions Draft → Under Review , 
Under Review → Published .
8) Action Logs
On successful validation/publish, log a summary line: 
TRANSPARENCY_OK: sources={used:X, excluded:Y}, datasets=Z, 
lastcheck=ISO8601
On block, log TRANSPARENCY_FAIL with reasons (not field contents).
9) Email Templates (optional)
tpl_transparency_missing : sent to Author when editor attempts to move
forward but fields missing.
